{"type":"message","id":"ba7de1bd","parentId":"0165f9c1","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:24:16.208Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户在问如何在本地配置 OpenClaw。我需要根据提供的技能列表和上下文来回答这个问题。\n\n从 `available_skills` 中，我看到有一个 `channels-setup` 技能，其描述是：\n\"Guide to set up and configure IM channels(Telegram, Discord, Slack, Feishu(飞书), Dingtalk(钉钉), Weibo(微博), 企业微信智能机器人, 个人微信 and more for OpenClaw。\"\n\n这看起来是最相关的技能。我应该读取这个技能的 SKILL.md 文件来获取详细的配置指南。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_wb0EG8vCd4GErpFIUr6yrpVv","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"~/.openclaw/skills/channels-setup/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":1940,"output":140,"cacheRead":29696,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31776,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776068646910}}
{"type":"message","id":"aa3fa810","parentId":"ba7de1bd","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:24:16.246Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_wb0EG8vCd4GErpFIUr6yrpVv","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: channels-setup\ndescription: Guide to set up and configure IM channels(Telegram, Discord, Slack, Feishu(飞书), Dingtalk(钉钉), Weibo(微博), 企业微信智能机器人, 个人微信 and more for OpenClaw.\n---\n\n## Quick Start\n\nUse openclaw CLI to enable and configure the channels you want.\n\nAfter configuration, you should restart the gateway to apply changes:\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\nBefore restarting, you must explicitly inform the user that OpenClaw is about to restart.\n\nIf the restart doesn’t take effect, guide the user to:\n\n1. Open Kimi Claw Web\n2. Click the settings button\n3. Manually restart Kimi Claw\n\nOn the Kimi Claw Web interface, the settings button is located in the top-right corner. In the mobile app, user can find the settings button at the top-right of the bottom input field.\n\nNotes:\n\n1. If users are unsure how to configure channels, direct them to the Settings -> [User Manual](https://kimiclaw.feishu.cn/wiki/W2o6wf94ViOrLnklVsvcCB2CnPd) in Kimi Claw Web for detailed instructions.\n2. Maintain brand exclusivity and channel-specific focus. When a user is configuring or deploying a specific channel (e.g., WeCom), strictly avoid mentioning any competing platforms or unrelated third-party services (e.g., Feishu).\n\n### Telegram\n\n```bash\nopenclaw config set channels.telegram.botToken \"YOUR_BOT_TOKEN\"\nopenclaw config set channels.telegram.dmPolicy \"pairing\"\nopenclaw config set channels.telegram.groups.\"*\".requireMention true\nopenclaw config set channels.telegram.enabled true\n```\n\n### Discord\n\n```bash\nopenclaw config set channels.discord.token \"YOUR_BOT_TOKEN\"\nopenclaw config set channels.discord.enabled true\n```\n\n### Slack\n\n```bash\nopenclaw config set channels.slack.mode \"socket\"\nopenclaw config set channels.slack.appToken \"xapp-...\"\nopenclaw config set channels.slack.botToken \"xoxb-...\"\nopenclaw config set channels.slack.enabled true\n```\n\n### 个人微信\n\n告诉用户可以使用 Kimi Claw 的一键接入功能快速接入个人微信机器人。路径为：点击 Kimi Claw 设置按钮，找到「聊天频道」，点击\n「+ 接入聊天软件」，选择「微信」即可。点击之后会弹出二维码，用手机微信扫码，可以快速创建飞书机器人。\n\n提示用户需要特定版本（>= 8.0.70）的微信才能使用个人微信机器人功能：\n\n### Feishu\n\n### 方式一（优先）\n\n优先告诉用户可以用 Kimi Claw 的一键接入功能快速接入飞书机器人。路径为：点击 Kimi Claw 设置按钮，找到「聊天频道」，点击\n「+ 接入聊天软件」，选择「飞书」即可。点击之后会弹出二维码，用飞书扫码，可以快速创建飞书机器人。\n\n### 方式二（过时，优先采用方式一）\n\n```bash\nopenclaw config set channels.feishu.appId \"YOUR_APP_ID\"\nopenclaw config set channels.feishu.appSecret \"YOUR_APP_SECRET\"\nopenclaw config set channels.feishu.groupPolicy \"open\"\nopenclaw config set channels.feishu.enabled true\nopenclaw config set channels.feishu.dmPolicy \"pairing\"\nopenclaw config set channels.feishu.requireMention true\n```\n\n### Dingtalk\n\nEdit the `channels` and `gateway` fields in `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` as below:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"channels\": {\n    \"dingtalk-connector\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"clientId\": \"dingxxxxxxxxx\",       // DingTalk Client ID (原 AppKey 和 SuiteKey)\n      \"clientSecret\": \"your_secret_here\", // DingTalk  (原 AppSecret 和 SuiteSecret)\n      \"gatewayToken\": \"\",                 // Optional: Gateway authentication token, the value of gateway.auth.token in openclaw.json\n      \"gatewayPassword\": \"\",              // Optional: Gateway authentication password (choose either token or password)\n      \"sessionTimeout\": 1800000           // Optional: Session timeout (ms), default is 30 minutes\n    }\n  },\n  \"gateway\": {\n    \"http\": {\n      \"endpoints\": {\n        \"chatCompletions\": {\n          \"enabled\": true\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n> If `/root/.openclaw/extensions` don't have `dingtalk-connector` directory, please install the plugin first:\n> \n> ```bash\n> openclaw plugins install @dingtalk-real-ai/dingtalk-connector\n> ```\n\n### Weibo\n\nWhen user wants to integrate Weibo, tell user the guide.\n\nConfig Weibo direct message channel:\n\n1. Open Weibo App, send message `连接龙虾` to [@微博龙虾助手](https://weibo.com/u/6808810981);\n2. `微博龙虾助手` will give user appid and appsecret, for example:\n\n```\n您的应用凭证信息如下：\n\nAppId: your-app-id\nAppSecret: your-app-secret\n```\n\n3. Config openclaw:\n\n```\nopenclaw config set 'channels.weibo.appSecret' 'your-appSecret'\nopenclaw config set 'channels.weibo.appId' 'your-appId'\n```\n\n4. If user wants to reset the appid and appsecret, send `重置凭证` to `微博龙虾助手`.\n\n> If `/root/.openclaw/extensions` don't have `weibo` directory, please install the plugin first:\n> \n> ```bash\n> git clone https://gitee.com/wecode-ai/openclaw-weibo.git\n> cd openclaw-weibo\n> openclaw plugins install .\n> openclaw gateway restart\n> ```\n\n## 企业微信智能机器人\n\n### 方式一（优先）\n\n优先告诉用户可以用 Kimi Claw 的一键接入功能快速接入企业微信智能机器人。路径为：点击 Kimi Claw 设置按钮，找到「聊天频道」，点击\n「+ 接入聊天软件」，选择「企业微信」即可。点击之后会弹出二维码，用企业微信扫码，可以快速创建企业微信智能机器人。\n\n### 方式二（过时，优先采用方式一）\n\nAsk the user to create `企业微信智能机器人` in [企业微信智能机器人](https://work.weixin.qq.com/wework_admin/frame#/aiHelper/create), and provide the `BotId` and `Secret`.\n\n```bash\nopenclaw config set channels.wecom.botId \"YOUR_BOT_ID\"\nopenclaw config set channels.wecom.secret \"YOUR_SECRET\"\nopenclaw config set channels.wecom.enabled true\n```\n\n### 插件安装与更新\n\n> If `/root/.openclaw/extensions` don't have `wecom-openclaw-plugin` directory, please install the plugin first:\n> \n> ```bash\n> openclaw plugins install @wecom/wecom-openclaw-plugin\n> ```\n\nTo update the plugin, you can run:\n\n```bash\nopenclaw plugins update wecom-openclaw-plugin\n```\n\n## References\n\nYou can refer to the following documents for more detailed configuration instructions:\n\nFor Feishu channel detail setup, please refer to:\n\n- [Feishu Channel Setup Guide](/root/.openclaw/extensions/feishu/README.md)\n\nFor Dingtalk channel detail setup, please refer to:\n\n- [Dingtalk Channel Setup Guide](/root/.openclaw/extensions/dingtalk-connector/README.md)\n\nFor Weibo channel detail setup, please refer to:\n\n- [Weibo Channel Setup Guide](/root/.openclaw/extensions/weibo/README.md)\n\nFor Wecom AI Bot channel detail setup, please refer to:\n\n- [Wecom AI Bot Channel Setup Guide](/root/.openclaw/extensions/wecom-openclaw-plugin/README.md)\n\nFor Telegram, Slack, Discord or more channels setup, please refer to [OpenClaw Channel Setup Guide](https://docs.openclaw.ai/channels). Explore `https://docs.openclaw.ai/channels` to see all available channel setup guides.\n\nIf users are unsure how to configure channels, direct them to the Settings -> [User Manual](https://kimiclaw.feishu.cn/wiki/W2o6wf94ViOrLnklVsvcCB2CnPd) in Kimi Claw Web for detailed instructions."}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776068656241}}
{"type":"message","id":"436ebbcd","parentId":"aa3fa810","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:24:37.106Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我已经了解了 OpenClaw 的配置方法。让我为用户总结主要的配置方式：\n\n1. 最快的配置方式是通过 Kimi Claw Web 界面一键接入\n2. 命令行配置方式针对不同平台（Telegram、Discord、Slack、飞书、钉钉、微博、企业微信等）\n\n根据用户的问题\"我本地有openclaw 如何配置呢\"，我应该给出一个清晰的回答，包括：\n1. 最简单的方法（Kimi Claw 一键接入）\n2. 各个平台的命令行配置方式\n3. 配置完成后需要重启 gateway\n\n由于用户没有指定具体要配置哪个平台，我应该给出一个概览，让他们选择。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"OpenClaw 配置分两种方式：\n\n## 最快方式（推荐）\n\n如果你用 Kimi Claw Web 界面，直接点**设置按钮** → 「聊天频道」→「+ 接入聊天软件」，扫码即可快速接入：\n- 微信个人号\n- 飞书机器人\n- 企业微信机器人\n\n## 命令行配置\n\n各平台配置命令如下，配完后需重启：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n**Telegram**\n```bash\nopenclaw config set channels.telegram.botToken \"你的BotToken\"\nopenclaw config set channels.telegram.enabled true\n```\n\n**Discord**\n```bash\nopenclaw config set channels.discord.token \"你的BotToken\"\nopenclaw config set channels.discord.enabled true\n```\n\n**Slack**\n```bash\nopenclaw config set channels.slack.mode \"socket\"\nopenclaw config set channels.slack.appToken \"xapp-...\"\nopenclaw config set channels.slack.botToken \"xoxb-...\"\nopenclaw config set channels.slack.enabled true\n```\n\n**飞书**（手动方式）\n```bash\nopenclaw config set channels.feishu.appId \"你的AppID\"\nopenclaw config set channels.feishu.appSecret \"你的AppSecret\"\nopenclaw config set channels.feishu.enabled true\n```\n\n**钉钉**\n需编辑 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` 的 `channels.dingtalk-connector` 字段，配置 clientId 和 clientSecret。\n\n**微博**\n私信 [@微博龙虾助手](https://weibo.com/u/6808810981) 发送「连接龙虾」获取 AppId 和 AppSecret，然后配置。\n\n---\n\n你要配置哪个平台？我可以给你更具体的步骤。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":2058,"output":504,"cacheRead":31488,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34050,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776068656247}}
{"type":"message","id":"ec204407","parentId":"436ebbcd","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:39:17.373Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"User Message From Kimi:\nsk-kimi-zEyiaeDhY865dQokCxZK0ziXvm6tJjJHf6YItszg3wftZV88pp2x7XA0RBho8MCK --为什么这个key 无法使用呢 hongzhang@MBP-HTM6NNMWC5-2102  ~/.openclaw   main  curl -s https://api.moonshot.cn/v1/models \\\n -H \"Authorization: Bearer sk-kimi-zEyiaeDhY865dQokCxZK0ziXvm6tJjJHf6YItszg3wftZV88pp2x7XA0RBho8MCK\"\n{\"error\":{\"message\":\"Invalid Authentication\",\"type\":\"invalid_authentication_error\"}}%\n<KIMI_REF type=\"file\" path=\"/root/.openclaw/workspace/.kimi/downloads/19d85fe8-3d02-8de5-8000-0000bd814ce3_image.png\" name=\"image.png\" id=\"19d85fe8-3d02-8de5-8000-0000bd814ce3\" />"}],"timestamp":1776069557368}}
{"type":"message","id":"a57af7e7","parentId":"ec204407","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:39:45.191Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户提供了一个 API key，但调用 Moonshot API 时返回了 \"Invalid Authentication\" 错误。我需要帮用户排查这个问题。\n\n可能的原因：\n1. API key 格式问题（看起来是一个标准的 sk- 开头的 key）\n2. API key 已过期或被撤销\n3. 用户可能复制时包含了额外字符（比如空格）\n4. Moonshot API 的 endpoint 或认证方式有变化\n5. 这个 key 可能不是 Moonshot 的，而是其他平台的（比如 OpenAI 兼容格式的 key）\n\n让我检查一下这个 key 的情况，并给用户提供排查建议。\n\n从截图中我可以看到用户在终端中执行了 curl 命令，返回了认证错误。\n\n我应该：\n1. 确认 key 的基本格式\n2. 提供排查步骤\n3. 建议用户检查 key 的来源和有效性","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"这个错误表示**认证失败**。几个可能的原因：\n\n## 1. Key 本身无效\n\n- Key 可能已过期、被撤销，或从未激活\n- 检查这个 Key 是否来自 Moonshot 开放平台（https://platform.moonshot.cn/）\n\n## 2. 检查 Key 完整性\n\n复制时可能带了空格或换行。验证：\n\n```bash\necho \"sk-kimi-zEyiaeDhY865dQokCxZK0ziXvm6tJjJHf6YItszg3wftZV88pp2x7XA0RBho8MCK\" | wc -c\n```\n\n正常应该是 83 个字符（含 `sk-kimi-` 前缀）。\n\n## 3. 确认 Key 所属平台\n\nMoonshot API Key 格式通常是 `sk-` 开头。如果你确定这是 Moonshot 的 Key，直接在他们控制台测试：\n\n```bash\ncurl -s https://api.moonshot.cn/v1/chat/completions \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer sk-kimi-你的key\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"model\": \"kimi-k2.5\",\n    \"messages\": [{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"你好\"}]\n  }'\n```\n\n## 4. 如果是给其他系统用\n\n确保系统支持 Moonshot 的 API 格式（OpenAI 兼容）。OpenClaw 配置 Moonshot 时需要在 `openclaw.json` 中指定：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"models\": {\n    \"kimi-k2.5\": {\n      \"provider\": \"openai\",\n      \"baseURL\": \"https://api.moonshot.cn/v1\",\n      \"apiKey\": \"sk-kimi-...\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n**最可能的结论**：这个 Key 本身已失效。去 Moonshot 控制台重新生成一个试试。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":4370,"output":578,"cacheRead":29696,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34644,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776069557372}}
{"type":"message","id":"b43c41d1","parentId":"a57af7e7","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:42:25.249Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"User Message From Kimi:\n这个key 没失效"}],"timestamp":1776069745240}}
{"type":"message","id":"bd40c9e0","parentId":"b43c41d1","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:42:45.358Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户坚持说这个key没有失效。让我再仔细看看可能的原因。\n\n错误信息是 \"Invalid Authentication\"，这通常意味着：\n1. Key确实无效（但用户说没失效）\n2. Key被错误地复制/粘贴（有隐藏字符、空格等）\n3. 请求头格式有问题\n4. 可能不是Moonshot的key，而是其他平台的key\n\n让我再检查一下：\n- Key格式是 sk-kimi-...，这看起来是Moonshot的格式\n- 用户用curl测试models端点返回401\n\n可能的问题：\n1. Key前面或后面有空格\n2. Key被截断了\n3. 这个Key可能是其他平台的（比如OpenAI、Azure等），但用户以为是Moonshot的\n\n我应该建议用户：\n1. 检查是否有隐藏字符\n2. 确认这个Key确实是Moonshot平台的\n3. 尝试在其他环境测试这个Key\n\n另外，用户可能混淆了不同平台的API Key。比如这个Key可能是OpenAI的，但用户在向Moonshot的API发请求。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"那问题出在**请求头格式**或**隐藏字符**。\n\n试试这个排查步骤：\n\n## 1. 检查隐藏字符\n\n```bash\n# 把 key 存到变量，再打印看长度\nKEY=\"sk-kimi-zEyiaeDhY865dQokCxZK0ziXvm6tJjJHf6YItszg3wftZV88pp2x7XA0RBho8MCK\"\necho \"$KEY\" | od -c | tail -5\n```\n\n如果看到 `\\r` 或 `\\n`，说明有换行符污染。\n\n## 2. 确认 Key 所属平台\n\n这个 Key 确实是 `sk-kimi-` 开头，但再确认一下：\n\n- 登录 https://platform.moonshot.cn/console/api-keys\n- 确认这个完整的 Key 字符串在列表里存在\n\n## 3. 直接用变量测试\n\n```bash\nKEY=\"sk-kimi-zEyiaeDhY865dQokCxZK0ziXvm6tJjJHf6YItszg3wftZV88pp2x7XA0RBho8MCK\"\ncurl -s https://api.moonshot.cn/v1/models \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $KEY\"\n```\n\n如果这样成功，说明之前手动输入时带入了不可见字符。\n\n## 4. 一个 Key 可能对应多个平台？\n\n确认这个 Key 不是在别的平台生成的（比如 OpenAI、Azure、或其他国内大模型厂商）。有些平台的 Key 也是 `sk-` 开头，但走不通 Moonshot 的 API。\n\n---\n\n试试第 3 步的变量方式。如果还是 401，那这个 Key 确实在 Moonshot 侧被拒绝，需要重新生成。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":442,"output":584,"cacheRead":34048,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35074,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776069745248}}
