{"type":"message","id":"1efc6879","parentId":"190910b8","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:49:57.571Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要自己执行 curl 命令来测试新 key。我需要提供完整的 curl 命令，包括测试模型列表和实际对话调用的示例。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"```bash\n# 测试1：列出模型（轻量验证）\ncurl -s https://api.moonshot.cn/v1/models \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer sk-ROWpgk4rEhQlVUxcCDPFECMT8vIxhysnST1wzAd7Cx8A4vqx\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 分隔线 ===\"\necho \"\"\n\n# 测试2：实际对话（完整验证）\ncurl -s https://api.moonshot.cn/v1/chat/completions \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer sk-ROWpgk4rEhQlVUxcCDPFECMT8vIxhysnST1wzAd7Cx8A4vqx\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"model\": \"kimi-k2.5\",\n    \"messages\": [{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"你好，测试一下\"}],\n    \"max_tokens\": 100\n  }'\n```"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":1366,"output":242,"cacheRead":35840,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37448,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776070183514}}
