{"type":"message","id":"94a8d22d","parentId":"ccad6739","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:51:15.269Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要针对 `api.kimi.com/coding/` 这个 baseUrl 和之前的 key 生成 curl 命令。\n\n从配置来看：\n- baseUrl: `https://api.kimi.com/coding/`\n- apiKey: `sk-kimi-zEyiaeDhY865dQokCxZK0ziXvm6tJjJHf6YItszg3wftZV88pp2x7XA0RBho8MCK`\n\n这是 Kimi Coding API，不是 Moonshot API。用户之前一直在用 Moonshot 的 endpoint 测试，但 key 是 Kimi Coding 的。\n\nKimi Coding API 的格式应该是 OpenAI 兼容的，endpoint 应该是 `/v1/chat/completions` 或类似的。\n\n让我生成正确的 curl。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"```bash\n# Kimi Coding API 测试\ncurl -s https://api.kimi.com/coding/v1/chat/completions \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer sk-kimi-zEyiaeDhY865dQokCxZK0ziXvm6tJjJHf6YItszg3wftZV88pp2x7XA0RBho8MCK\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"model\": \"kimi-k2.5\",\n    \"messages\": [{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"你好\"}]\n  }'\n```\n\n注意 `api.kimi.com/coding/` 和 `api.moonshot.cn` 是**不同的 API**。前面的 key 是给 Kimi Coding 用的，不是 Moonshot。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":382,"output":333,"cacheRead":37120,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37835,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776070261312}}
