{"type":"message","id":"1c244b7a","parentId":"6463c572","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:56:25.058Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问的是 `baseUrl` 是否需要 `/v1`。让我思考一下：\n\n1. Kimi Coding 的 API 地址是 `https://api.kimi.com/coding`\n2. 之前 curl 测试用的是 `https://api.kimi.com/coding/v1/chat/completions`\n3. OpenClaw 的 `openai-chat` API 类型通常会自动在 baseUrl 后追加 `/v1/chat/completions`\n\n所以 `baseUrl` 应该只写 `https://api.kimi.com/coding`，不要带 `/v1`。OpenClaw 会自动加上 `/v1/chat/completions`。\n\n如果用户带 `/v1`，可能会变成 `/coding/v1/v1/chat/completions`，导致 404。\n\n确认一下我的理解是正确的。对于 OpenAI 兼容的 API：\n- baseUrl: `https://api.kimi.com/coding`\n- OpenClaw 会自动追加 `/v1/chat/completions`\n\n所以不需要在 baseUrl 里写 `/v1`。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"不需要 `/v1`。\n\nOpenClaw 的 `openai-chat` 类型会**自动追加** `/v1/chat/completions`。\n\n如果你写成：\n```json\n\"baseUrl\": \"https://api.kimi.com/coding/v1\"\n```\n\n实际请求会变成：\n```\nhttps://api.kimi.com/coding/v1/v1/chat/completions\n```\n\n导致 404。\n\n所以保持：\n```json\n\"baseUrl\": \"https://api.kimi.com/coding\"\n```\n\nOpenClaw 会自动处理成正确的 `/v1/chat/completions` 路径。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":1437,"output":325,"cacheRead":39424,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41186,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776070569414}}
{"type":"message","id":"1b6f7c5d","parentId":"1c244b7a","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:57:16.349Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"User Message From Kimi:\n(base) 🐍 base  hongzhang@MBP-HTM6NNMWC5-2102  ~/.openclaw   main  openclaw gateway restart\n\n🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.23-2 (7ffe7e4)\n iMessage green bubble energy, but for everyone.\n\nConfig invalid\nFile: ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\nProblem:\n - models.providers.kimi.api: Invalid option: expected one of \"openai-completions\"|\"openai-responses\"|\"openai-codex-responses\"|\"anthropic-messages\"|\"google-generative-ai\"|\"github-copilot\"|\"bedrock-converse-stream\"|\"ollama\"\n\nRun: openclaw doctor --fix\nGateway aborted: config is invalid.\nmodels.providers.kimi.api: Invalid option: expected one of \"openai-completions\"|\"openai-responses\"|\"openai-codex-responses\"|\"anthropic-messages\"|\"google-generative-ai\"|\"github-copilot\"|\"bedrock-converse-stream\"|\"ollama\"\nFix the config and retry, or run \"openclaw doctor\" to repair.\n(base) ✘  🐍 base  hongzhang@MBP-HTM6NNMWC5-2102  ~/.openclaw   main "}],"timestamp":1776070636344}}
{"type":"message","id":"b33829a4","parentId":"1b6f7c5d","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:57:56.855Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户遇到了配置错误。错误信息显示 `models.providers.kimi.api` 的值无效，期望的选项是：\n- \"openai-completions\"\n- \"openai-responses\"\n- \"openai-codex-responses\"\n- \"anthropic-messages\"\n- \"google-generative-ai\"\n- \"github-copilot\"\n- \"bedrock-converse-stream\"\n- \"ollama\"\n\n我之前建议的 \"openai-chat\" 不在列表中。我应该看看哪个是最合适的。\n\nKimi Coding API 是 OpenAI 兼容的，所以应该使用 \"openai-completions\" 或 \"openai-responses\"。\n\n根据 OpenAI 的 API：\n- `/v1/chat/completions` 是聊天补全接口\n- `/v1/responses` 是新的 Responses API\n\n\"openai-completions\" 应该对应 `/v1/chat/completions`，这正是我们需要的。\n\n让我修正配置。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"`openai-chat` 不对，要用 `openai-completions`：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"meta\": {\n    \"lastTouchedVersion\": \"2026.3.23-2\",\n    \"lastTouchedAt\": \"2026-04-13T07:04:34.455Z\"\n  },\n  \"wizard\": {\n    \"lastRunAt\": \"2026-04-13T07:04:34.434Z\",\n    \"lastRunVersion\": \"2026.3.23-2\",\n    \"lastRunCommand\": \"configure\",\n    \"lastRunMode\": \"local\"\n  },\n  \"models\": {\n    \"mode\": \"merge\",\n    \"providers\": {\n      \"kimi\": {\n        \"baseUrl\": \"https://api.kimi.com/coding\",\n        \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n        \"apiKey\": \"sk-kimi-zEyiaeDhY865dQokCxZK0ziXvm6tJjJHf6YItszg3wftZV88pp2x7XA0RBho8MCK\",\n        \"models\": [\n          {\n            \"id\": \"kimi-code\",\n            \"name\": \"Kimi Code\",\n            \"reasoning\": true,\n            \"input\": [\n              \"text\",\n              \"image\"\n            ],\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"input\": 0,\n              \"output\": 0,\n              \"cacheRead\": 0,\n              \"cacheWrite\": 0\n            },\n            \"contextWindow\": 262144,\n            \"maxTokens\": 32768\n          }\n        ]\n      },\n      \"zai\": {\n        \"baseUrl\": \"https://open.bigmodel.cn/api/paas/v4\",\n        \"api\": \"openai-responses\",\n        \"apiKey\": \"0ead4d69789e4ccdb7560d33b2314ec5.KU3Tajy5OVQ1g6ry\",\n        \"models\": [\n          {\n            \"id\": \"glm-5-turbo\",\n            \"name\": \"GLM-5 Turbo\",\n            \"reasoning\": true,\n            \"input\": [\n              \"text\",\n              \"image\"\n            ],\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"input\": 0,\n              \"output\": 0,\n              \"cacheRead\": 0,\n              \"cacheWrite\": 0\n            },\n            \"contextWindow\": 128000,\n            \"maxTokens\": 4096\n          }\n        ]\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"defaults\": {\n      \"model\": {\n        \"primary\": \"kimi/kimi-code\",\n        \"fallbacks\": [\n          \"zai/glm-5-turbo\"\n        ]\n      },\n      \"models\": {\n        \"kimi/kimi-code\": {\n          \"alias\": \"Kimi\"\n        },\n        \"zai/glm-5-turbo\": {\n          \"alias\": \"智谱\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"workspace\": \"/Users/hongzhang/.openclaw/workspace\",\n      \"compaction\": {\n        \"mode\": \"safeguard\"\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"tools\": {\n    \"profile\": \"coding\"\n  },\n  \"commands\": {\n    \"native\": \"auto\",\n    \"nativeSkills\": \"auto\",\n    \"restart\": true,\n    \"ownerDisplay\": \"raw\"\n  },\n  \"session\": {\n    \"dmScope\": \"per-channel-peer\"\n  },\n  \"channels\": {\n    \"openclaw-weixin\": {\n      \"accounts\": {}\n    }\n  },\n  \"gateway\": {\n    \"port\": 18789,\n    \"mode\": \"local\",\n    \"bind\": \"loopback\",\n    \"auth\": {\n      \"mode\": \"token\",\n      \"token\": \"9d2ac683de845b5b3cf30e4a3a4fa15c197c5e2a2ac07451\"\n    },\n    \"tailscale\": {\n      \"mode\": \"off\",\n      \"resetOnExit\": false\n    }\n  },\n  \"mcp\": {\n    \"servers\": {\n      \"openspace\": {\n        \"command\": \"openspace-mcp\",\n        \"env\": {\n          \"OPENSPACE_HOST_SKILL_DIRS\": \"/Users/hongzhang/.openclaw/skills\",\n          \"OPENSPACE_WORKSPACE\": \"/Users/hongzhang/.openclaw/workspace/OpenSpace\"\n        },\n        \"toolTimeout\": 600\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"skills\": {\n    \"load\": {\n      \"extraDirs\": [\n        \"/Users/hongzhang/.openclaw/myskills\"\n      ]\n    }\n  },\n  \"plugins\": {\n    \"allow\": [\n      \"openclaw-weixin\"\n    ],\n    \"entries\": {\n      \"openclaw-weixin\": {\n        \"enabled\": true\n      }\n    },\n    \"installs\": {\n      \"openclaw-weixin\": {\n        \"source\": \"npm\",\n        \"spec\": \"@tencent-weixin/openclaw-weixin@latest\",\n        \"installPath\": \"/Users/hongzhang/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-weixin\",\n        \"version\": \"2.0.1\",\n        \"resolvedName\": \"@tencent-weixin/openclaw-weixin\",\n        \"resolvedVersion\": \"2.0.1\",\n        \"resolvedSpec\": \"@tencent-weixin/openclaw-weixin@2.0.1\",\n        \"integrity\": \"sha512-Ib7onvLU8a1ox9craMZxPwrN+ffJQJbToZzeMwoYryBOMIoBlVY0oCuQF7BZvZ7GRQQKOSSAdxvFkO47hKu0rg==\",\n        \"shasum\": \"06339fdc83226454e1286221889fd62c76ae2463\",\n        \"resolvedAt\": \"2026-03-25T12:09:25.063Z\",\n        \"installedAt\": \"2026-03-25T12:09:33.928Z\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n改动：`api` 从 `\"openai-chat\"` 改为 `\"openai-completions\"`。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":602,"output":1497,"cacheRead":40704,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42803,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776070636349}}
{"type":"message","id":"64106fa2","parentId":"b33829a4","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:59:00.524Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"User Message From Kimi:\n如何确定openclaw gateway 重启后的状态是正常的"}],"timestamp":1776070740519}}
{"type":"message","id":"b7c540bd","parentId":"64106fa2","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:59:13.014Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想知道如何确认 OpenClaw gateway 重启后的状态是否正常。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"## 验证 gateway 状态的几种方式\n\n### 1. 命令行状态检查\n\n```bash\n# 查看 gateway 是否在运行\nopenclaw gateway status\n\n# 详细诊断\nopenclaw doctor\n```\n\n### 2. 查看日志\n\n```bash\n# 直接查看日志输出（前台运行时可看到）\nopenclaw gateway start\n\n# 或查看后台日志（如果有日志文件）\ntail -f ~/.openclaw/logs/gateway.log\n```\n\n### 3. 测试 API 连通性\n\n```bash\n# 测试 gateway 是否响应\ncurl http://127.0.0.1:18789/health\n# 或\ncurl http://localhost:18789/status\n```\n\n### 4. 发送测试消息\n\n在配置好的 channel（如微信、Telegram 等）里发一条消息，看是否能正常回复。\n\n### 5. 查看配置是否正确加载\n\n```bash\nopenclaw config get models\nopenclaw config get agents.defaults.model\n```\n\n---\n\n**正常状态的标志：**\n- `openclaw gateway status` 显示 `running`\n- 日志没有报错（特别是没有 `Config invalid` 或连接失败）\n- 测试消息能收到回复\n\n你现在重启后的输出是什么？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":1423,"output":282,"cacheRead":41216,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42921,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776070740523}}
{"type":"message","id":"ed9b4e73","parentId":"b7c540bd","timestamp":"2026-04-13T09:00:32.904Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"User Message From Kimi:\n为什么会报这个\n<KIMI_REF type=\"file\" path=\"/root/.openclaw/workspace/.kimi/downloads/19d86122-2342-8e38-8000-0000dc5d824f_image.png\" name=\"image.png\" id=\"19d86122-2342-8e38-8000-0000dc5d824f\" />"}],"timestamp":1776070832895}}
{"type":"message","id":"78bd6112","parentId":"ed9b4e73","timestamp":"2026-04-13T09:06:09.441Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这个错误信息很关键：\n- `429 You exceeded your current quota, please check your plan and billing details`\n- `Insufficient balance` (余额不足)\n\n这说明 Kimi Coding API 的 key 本身没问题，**但是账户余额不足或配额用完了**。\n\n用户说他在 Kimi Claw 里能正常使用，但那是走的 Kimi Claw 自己的套餐/授权，不是用这个 key 直接调用 API。\n\n当 OpenClaw 用这个 key 直接请求 `api.kimi.com/coding` 时，走的是**按量计费**模式，而用户账户里没有额度或额度用完了。\n\n这不是配置问题，是**付费/额度问题**。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"余额不足。\n\n`429 Insufficient balance` 表示你的 Kimi Coding API 账户**没有可用额度**。\n\n## 原因\n\nKimi Claw 和 Kimi Coding API 是两套计费体系：\n\n- **Kimi Claw**：你看到的\"套餐\"是 Kimi Claw 的订阅，key 由平台托管\n- **Kimi Coding API**（`api.kimi.com/coding`）：需要单独充值，按量计费\n\n你的 key 能认证通过，但请求时被拒绝，说明账户余额为 0 或没有开通付费。\n\n## 解决方案\n\n### 方案1：给 Kimi Coding API 充值\n去 https://platform.moonshot.cn 或相关入口充值，获取 API 调用额度。\n\n### 方案2：改用其他 provider\n你的配置里已经有 `zai`（智谱）且是正常的，可以临时切过去：\n\n```json\n\"agents\": {\n  \"defaults\": {\n    \"model\": {\n      \"primary\": \"zai/glm-5-turbo\",\n      \"fallbacks\": []\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 方案3：确认是否真的要用 Kimi Coding API\n如果你只是想在 OpenClaw 里用 Kimi 模型，可能不需要自己配 key。Kimi Claw 本身是已接入的状态，可以直接用。\n\n---\n\n**确认一下**：你是要在 OpenClaw 里用自己的 Kimi key，还是想让 OpenClaw 调用 Kimi Claw 已经配好的模型？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":13305,"output":447,"cacheRead":29696,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43448,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776070832903}}
{"type":"message","id":"d2189fdd","parentId":"78bd6112","timestamp":"2026-04-13T09:09:51.426Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"User Message From Kimi:\n我订阅了这个套餐，无法在openclaw 中使用吗\n<KIMI_REF type=\"file\" path=\"/root/.openclaw/workspace/.kimi/downloads/19d861a5-b8f2-8d5c-8000-0000837fe4aa_image.png\" name=\"image.png\" id=\"19d861a5-b8f2-8d5c-8000-0000837fe4aa\" />"}],"timestamp":1776071391421}}
{"type":"message","id":"5e32baae","parentId":"d2189fdd","timestamp":"2026-04-13T09:10:07.011Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户订阅了 Kimi 的\"AI 编程无限卡\"套餐，但无法在 OpenClaw 中使用。这是因为：\n\n1. 用户订阅的是 **Kimi Claw / Kimi 官方平台的套餐**，这个套餐的 key 是由 Kimi Claw 平台托管的\n2. 用户配置的 `api.kimi.com/coding` 是 **Kimi Coding API**，这是一个独立的 API 服务，需要单独的 API 额度\n\n这两者是不同的体系：\n- Kimi Claw 的套餐：通过 Kimi Claw Web/App 使用，key 不直接暴露给用户\n- Kimi Coding API：需要单独申请和充值，按量计费\n\n所以用户的套餐无法直接用于 OpenClaw 的配置。需要在 OpenClaw 中使用 Kimi Claw 的方式，或者单独给 Kimi Coding API 充值。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"不能直接用。\n\n你订阅的是 **Kimi Claw 套餐**，但 OpenClaw 里配的是 **Kimi Coding API**，这是两套独立的系统：\n\n| 服务 | 你的套餐 | 计费方式 |\n|------|---------|---------|\n| **Kimi Claw** (Web/App) | ✅ 有无限卡 | 平台托管，你无感知 |\n| **Kimi Coding API** (`api.kimi.com/coding`) | ❌ 未开通 | 需单独充值，按量付费 |\n\n你的套餐只在 Kimi Claw 官方渠道有效，key 由平台托管，不暴露给你。\n\n## 想在 OpenClaw 里用 Kimi，有两个选择：\n\n### 方案1：给 Kimi Coding API 单独充值\n去平台开通 API 额度，才能用你自己的 key 调用。\n\n### 方案2：让 OpenClaw 走 Kimi Claw 的通道\n如果你要让 OpenClaw 调用你已经订阅的 Kimi 服务，需要配成 **Kimi Claw 的接入方式**，而不是直接配 `api.kimi.com/coding`。\n\n但这通常需要 Kimi Claw 提供专门的接入方式（如 MCP 或代理），而不是直接用 API key。\n\n---\n\n**结论**：你的套餐和 OpenClaw 目前配的不是同一个东西，无法互通。要么给 Coding API 充值，要么改用其他方式接入 Kimi。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":668,"output":467,"cacheRead":42752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43887,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776071391426}}
