{"type":"message","id":"fa713c22","parentId":"ae0f6926","timestamp":"2026-04-13T09:14:40.511Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想知道如何让 OpenClaw 走 Kimi Claw 的通道，而不是直接调用 Kimi Coding API。\n\nKimi Claw 是一个桌面/移动应用，它本身提供 AI 对话能力。要让 OpenClaw 接入 Kimi Claw，需要了解 Kimi Claw 是否提供某种外部接入方式，比如：\n1. MCP (Model Context Protocol)\n2. 本地 API 代理\n3. 其他集成方式\n\n让我搜索一下相关信息，或者看看是否有相关的配置方式。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"让我确认一下 Kimi Claw 是否支持外部接入。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_Il9uYRcHYYPEkMH5YFgT43rj","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"Kimi Claw MCP OpenClaw 接入 配置"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":480,"output":146,"cacheRead":43264,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43890,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776071671615}}
