{"type":"message","id":"ee89a7cd","parentId":"01cda5bd","timestamp":"2026-04-13T09:20:48.640Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户充值了 Moonshot 平台的余额。但之前测试的错误是：\n\n```\n{\"error\":{\"message\":\"Kimi For Coding is currently only available for Coding Agents such as Kimi CLI, Claude Code, Roo Code, Kilo Code, etc.\",\"type\":\"access_terminated_error\"}}\n```\n\n这个错误不是余额问题，而是客户端限制问题。即使有余额，Kimi Coding API 也只允许特定的客户端使用。\n\n用户现在有余额了，但 key 的访问限制依然存在。需要解释这个情况，并建议切换到标准的 Moonshot API（api.moonshot.cn）而不是 Kimi Coding API（api.kimi.com/coding）。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"充值成功，但问题没变。\n\n之前的错误不是余额问题：\n\n```\nKimi For Coding is currently only available for Coding Agents such as Kimi CLI, Claude Code, Roo Code, Kilo Code, etc.\n```\n\n这是**客户端白名单限制**。Kimi Coding API 只允许特定工具接入，OpenClaw 不在名单里。即使有余额，也会报这个错。\n\n## 解决方案\n\n改用标准的 **Moonshot API**，而不是 Kimi Coding API：\n\n### 修改配置\n\n```json\n{\n  \"providers\": {\n    \"moonshot\": {\n      \"baseUrl\": \"https://api.moonshot.cn/v1\",\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"apiKey\": \"sk-kimi-zEyiaeDhY865dQokCxZK0ziXvm6tJjJHf6YItszg3wftZV88pp2x7XA0RBho8MCK\",\n      \"models\": [\n        {\n          \"id\": \"kimi-k2.5\",\n          \"name\": \"Kimi K2.5\"\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n同时更新默认模型：\n```json\n\"agents\": {\n  \"defaults\": {\n    \"model\": {\n      \"primary\": \"moonshot/kimi-k2.5\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 先测试 API 是否通\n\n```bash\ncurl -s https://api.moonshot.cn/v1/chat/completions \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer sk-kimi-zEyiaeDhY865dQokCxZK0ziXvm6tJjJHf6YItszg3wftZV88pp2x7XA0RBho8MCK\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"model\": \"kimi-k2.5\", \"messages\": [{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"你好\"}]}'\n```\n\n如果返回正常响应（不是 `access_terminated_error`），说明可以用。然后改配置、重启 gateway。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":551,"output":558,"cacheRead":45056,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46165,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776072029458}}
