{"type":"message","id":"45df9c2a","parentId":"25d9c580","timestamp":"2026-04-13T09:22:13.230Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这个 key 有效，是 Moonshot API 的 key（不是 Kimi Coding）。返回了所有模型列表，包括 kimi-k2.5。\n\n现在可以给用户配置使用这个 key。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"这个 key **有效**，是标准 Moonshot API。\n\n配置用这个：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"meta\": {\n    \"lastTouchedVersion\": \"2026.3.23-2\",\n    \"lastTouchedAt\": \"2026-04-13T07:04:34.455Z\"\n  },\n  \"wizard\": {\n    \"lastRunAt\": \"2026-04-13T07:04:34.434Z\",\n    \"lastRunVersion\": \"2026.3.23-2\",\n    \"lastRunCommand\": \"configure\",\n    \"lastRunMode\": \"local\"\n  },\n  \"models\": {\n    \"mode\": \"merge\",\n    \"providers\": {\n      \"moonshot\": {\n        \"baseUrl\": \"https://api.moonshot.cn/v1\",\n        \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n        \"apiKey\": \"sk-zQ32N7dhJKuUpSodZwAvLjUfze1t9pvjWtTK7OC6WYZzzWr8\",\n        \"models\": [\n          {\n            \"id\": \"kimi-k2.5\",\n            \"name\": \"Kimi K2.5\",\n            \"reasoning\": true,\n            \"input\": [\"text\", \"image\"],\n            \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0},\n            \"contextWindow\": 262144,\n            \"maxTokens\": 32768\n          }\n        ]\n      },\n      \"zai\": {\n        \"baseUrl\": \"https://open.bigmodel.cn/api/paas/v4\",\n        \"api\": \"openai-responses\",\n        \"apiKey\": \"0ead4d69789e4ccdb7560d33b2314ec5.KU3Tajy5OVQ1g6ry\",\n        \"models\": [\n          {\n            \"id\": \"glm-5-turbo\",\n            \"name\": \"GLM-5 Turbo\",\n            \"reasoning\": true,\n            \"input\": [\"text\", \"image\"],\n            \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0},\n            \"contextWindow\": 128000,\n            \"maxTokens\": 4096\n          }\n        ]\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"defaults\": {\n      \"model\": {\n        \"primary\": \"moonshot/kimi-k2.5\",\n        \"fallbacks\": [\"zai/glm-5-turbo\"]\n      },\n      \"models\": {\n        \"moonshot/kimi-k2.5\": {\"alias\": \"Kimi\"},\n        \"zai/glm-5-turbo\": {\"alias\": \"智谱\"}\n      },\n      \"workspace\": \"/Users/hongzhang/.openclaw/workspace\",\n      \"compaction\": {\"mode\": \"safeguard\"}\n    }\n  },\n  \"tools\": {\"profile\": \"coding\"},\n  \"commands\": {\n    \"native\": \"auto\",\n    \"nativeSkills\": \"auto\",\n    \"restart\": true,\n    \"ownerDisplay\": \"raw\"\n  },\n  \"session\": {\"dmScope\": \"per-channel-peer\"},\n  \"channels\": {\"openclaw-weixin\": {\"accounts\": {}}},\n  \"gateway\": {\n    \"port\": 18789,\n    \"mode\": \"local\",\n    \"bind\": \"loopback\",\n    \"auth\": {\"mode\": \"token\", \"token\": \"9d2ac683de845b5b3cf30e4a3a4fa15c197c5e2a2ac07451\"},\n    \"tailscale\": {\"mode\": \"off\", \"resetOnExit\": false}\n  },\n  \"mcp\": {\n    \"servers\": {\n      \"openspace\": {\n        \"command\": \"openspace-mcp\",\n        \"env\": {\n          \"OPENSPACE_HOST_SKILL_DIRS\": \"/Users/hongzhang/.openclaw/skills\",\n          \"OPENSPACE_WORKSPACE\": \"/Users/hongzhang/.openclaw/workspace/OpenSpace\"\n        },\n        \"toolTimeout\": 600\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"skills\": {\"load\": {\"extraDirs\": [\"/Users/hongzhang/.openclaw/myskills\"]}},\n  \"plugins\": {\n    \"allow\": [\"openclaw-weixin\"],\n    \"entries\": {\"openclaw-weixin\": {\"enabled\": true}},\n    \"installs\": {\n      \"openclaw-weixin\": {\n        \"source\": \"npm\",\n        \"spec\": \"@tencent-weixin/openclaw-weixin@latest\",\n        \"installPath\": \"/Users/hongzhang/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-weixin\",\n        \"version\": \"2.0.1\",\n        \"resolvedName\": \"@tencent-weixin/openclaw-weixin\",\n        \"resolvedVersion\": \"2.0.1\",\n        \"resolvedSpec\": \"@tencent-weixin/openclaw-weixin@2.0.1\",\n        \"integrity\": \"sha512-Ib7onvLU8a1ox9craMZxPwrN+ffJQJbToZzeMwoYryBOMIoBlVY0oCuQF7BZvZ7GRQQKOSSAdxvFkO47hKu0rg==\",\n        \"shasum\": \"06339fdc83226454e1286221889fd62c76ae2463\",\n        \"resolvedAt\": \"2026-03-25T12:09:25.063Z\",\n        \"installedAt\": \"2026-03-25T12:09:33.928Z\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n改完重启：\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":993,"output":1254,"cacheRead":46080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48327,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776072097778}}
