{"type":"message","id":"5303dee8","parentId":"fac8d1f3","timestamp":"2026-04-13T11:33:09.684Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想把这个新的 Moonshot key 配到 `api.kimi.com/coding/` 的 URL 下。\n\n但之前我们验证过：\n1. `api.kimi.com/coding/` 是 Kimi Coding API\n2. 那个 key 报 `access_terminated_error`，说只允许特定客户端（Kimi CLI、Claude Code 等）\n3. 新给的 key `sk-zQ32N7dhJKuUpSodZwAvLjUfze1t9pvjWtTK7OC6WYZzzWr8` 在 `api.moonshot.cn` 是正常的\n\n问题是：这个新的 key 在 `api.kimi.com/coding/` 上会不会也报同样的客户端限制错误？\n\n让我先测试一下这个新 key 在 coding URL 上是否可用。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"先验证这个新 key 在 Kimi Coding URL 上是否可用："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_7VVHbKX2tn2pj470iDOsJxzF","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s https://api.kimi.com/coding/v1/models \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer sk-zQ32N7dhJKuUpSodZwAvLjUfze1t9pvjWtTK7OC6WYZzzWr8\"","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":18593,"output":259,"cacheRead":29696,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48548,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776079892865}}
{"type":"message","id":"ab704525","parentId":"5303dee8","timestamp":"2026-04-13T11:33:09.799Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_7VVHbKX2tn2pj470iDOsJxzF","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"error\":{\"message\":\"The API Key appears to be invalid or may have expired. Please verify your credentials and try again.\",\"type\":\"invalid_authentication_error\"}}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":101,"aggregated":"{\"error\":{\"message\":\"The API Key appears to be invalid or may have expired. Please verify your credentials and try again.\",\"type\":\"invalid_authentication_error\"}}","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776079989793}}
{"type":"message","id":"bbfad5ab","parentId":"ab704525","timestamp":"2026-04-13T11:33:22.068Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"果然，这个新 key 在 `api.kimi.com/coding` 上也是无效的。\n\n这说明：\n1. `api.moonshot.cn` 和 `api.kimi.com/coding` 是两套独立的 key 体系\n2. 在 `api.moonshot.cn` 能用的 key，在 `api.kimi.com/coding` 上不能用\n3. 反过来也一样\n\n所以用户不能把这个新 key 配到 `api.kimi.com/coding` 的 baseUrl 下，会报 401。\n\n我应该告诉他这个事实，并坚持让他用 `api.moonshot.cn/v1` 的配置。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"不行，这个 key 在 `api.kimi.com/coding` 上也是无效的。\n\n两套 API 的 key **不互通**：\n\n| API 地址 | 你的 key 是否可用 |\n|---------|----------------|\n| `api.moonshot.cn/v1` | ✅ 有效 |\n| `api.kimi.com/coding` | ❌ 无效 |\n\n所以只能用：\n\n```json\n\"baseUrl\": \"https://api.moonshot.cn/v1\"\n```\n\n不能用 `api.kimi.com/coding`。\n\n如果你坚持用 coding 的 URL，需要找 Kimi 申请专门的 Coding API key，那个 key 在 `api.moonshot.cn` 上也不能用。\n\n---\n\n**结论**：配置按我之前给的，用 `api.moonshot.cn/v1`，这个 key 能正常工作。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":469,"output":297,"cacheRead":48128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48894,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776079989800}}
{"type":"message","id":"27aaf34f","parentId":"bbfad5ab","timestamp":"2026-04-13T11:33:22.446Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"User Message From Kimi:\n[Buffered IM messages received while connector was catching up]\n[Buffered IM message 1/2]\ncurl -s https://api.moonshot.cn/v1/chat/completions \\\n -H \"Authorization: Bearer sk-kimi-zEyiaeDhY865dQokCxZK0ziXvm6tJjJHf6YItszg3wftZV88pp2x7XA0RBho8MCK\" \\\n -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n -d '{\"model\": \"kimi-k2.5\", \"messages\": [{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"你好\"}]}'\n\n\n[Buffered IM message 2/2]\nurl 换成这个baseUrl\": \"https://api.kimi.com/coding/ \","}],"timestamp":1776080002436}}
