{"type":"message","id":"361913df","parentId":"f1e6e265","timestamp":"2026-04-13T14:10:52.459Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The file doesn't exist, so I need to create it. I should store the key durable memories from the conversation summary. The most important things to remember:\n1. OpenClaw configuration: Kimi Coding API (`api.kimi.com/coding`) is whitelist-restricted and doesn't work with OpenClaw. Must use Moonshot API (`api.moonshot.cn/v1`) with `api: \"openai-completions\"`.\n2. Valid working Moonshot key for the user's setup.\n3. Default model configuration: `moonshot/kimi-k2.5` as primary, `zai/glm-5-turbo` as fallback.\n4. The `baseUrl` should not have trailing spaces.\n5. Gateway restart is required after config changes.\n\nI should keep it concise and factual.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_qBGroy8zLGaOqCQn2LWDqGwf","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 2026-04-13\n\n## OpenClaw Gateway 配置（Kimi / Moonshot）\n\n- **Kimi Coding API** (`https://api.kimi.com/coding`) 对客户端做了白名单限制，OpenClaw 不在允许列表内，返回 `access_terminated_error`。无法使用。\n- **可用方案**：改用标准 **Moonshot API** (`https://api.moonshot.cn/v1`)，provider `api` 字段必须填 `\"openai-completions\"`（OpenClaw 允许的枚举值之一）。\n- **有效 Key**：`sk-zQ32N7dhJKuUpSodZwAvLjUfze1t9pvjWtTK7OC6WYZzzWr8`（在 `api.moonshot.cn/v1` 验证通过）。\n- **智谱 fallback Key**：`0ead4d69789e4ccdb7560d33b2314ec5.KU3Tajy5OVQ1g6ry`\n- **当前默认模型**：主模型 `moonshot/kimi-k2.5`，fallback `zai/glm-5-turbo`。\n- **注意**：`baseUrl` 末尾不能带空格；修改 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` 后必须执行 `openclaw gateway restart` 才能生效。\n\n## 中矿资源 2025 年报关键数据\n\n- 津巴布韦 Bikita 矿山锂辉石浮选厂（200 万吨/年）年产约 **30 万吨锂辉石精矿**（Li2O ≥ 7.0%）。\n- 透锂长石重选厂（200 万吨/年）年产约 **30 万吨化学级透锂长石精矿**。\n- 截至 2025 年底，Bikita 矿区保有锂矿石资源量 12,409.39 万吨，Li2O 平均品位 0.95%，折合 LCE 292.40 万吨。\n\n","file_path":"memory/2026-04-13.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":621,"output":634,"cacheRead":48640,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":498