{"type":"message","id":"5932cbd9","parentId":"3b8d94a4","timestamp":"2026-04-13T14:16:56.855Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户发送了一张图片，我需要先读取图片内容，看看是什么。然后结合之前的问题，用户问的是\"按当前最新的价格计算，2026年大概多少利润，前瞻PE多少\"。\n\n从前面的对话看，用户在问藏格矿业、紫金矿业（他误写成了\"资金\"）的对比。现在他发了一张图片，可能是股票行情截图，我需要先读取图片来确认是哪只股票的价格信息。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_3u8c5iqnPud5ikWFZx0tm11s","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/.kimi/downloads/19d87337-3fc2-801a-8000-00000cea2349_image.png"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":18629,"output":138,"cacheRead":49408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68175,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776089806677}}
